Title: Nightwalkers
Plot: Carter, Teal'c and Jonas investigate the death of a scientist with connections to the Goa'uld, and find a small town whose citizens harbor a dark secret.
GuestStars: Dave 'Squatch' Ward, Blu Mankuma, Peter DeLuise, Vincent Gale, Sean Tyson, Michael Eklund, Peter Anderson, Scott Moneil, Carin Moffat, Christie Wilkes, Adrian Holmes
